avy caribbean patrol for channel five and national geographic in 0 terrill returned to working with the royal marines when he joined  commando in the dangerous nad e ali north district of helmand province this was for a part series commissioned by channel five entitled royal marines mission afghanistan transmitted in januaryfebruary 0 in late 0 terrill embarked on a project that brought together the military and the theatre the theatre royal haymarket where terrill had filmed theatreland in 00 put on a play using injured soldiers and marines as the actors singers and dancers the play written by the poet owen sheers and based on the experiences of the soldiers mostly in afghanistan was called the two worlds of charlie f and was performed on  january 0 terrills featurelength film entitled theatre of war documenting the preparation of the play was shown on bbcs imagine strand and was nominated for a prestigious grierson award in the best arts documentary category in 0 terrills current affairs film for the bbc marine a criminal or casualty of war won the evcom clarion award for ethics in journalism in 0 terrill became a fellow of the maritime foundation and was presented with a lifetime achievement award terrill lectures widely on film making techniques – especially on working solo in the field he holds regular workshops at the london film school personal lifeedit in  terrill was engaged for a brief period to former glamour model heather mills he proposed to her on a fishing boat whilst sailing up the mekong river in cambodia where they were making a film about landmines terrill is now married to the bafta awardwinning filmmaker christine hall on  february 0 terrill received a full apology in open court from news group for repeatedly hacking his phone in 000 they also paid undisclosed but substantial damages plus costs terrill is an accomplished amateur athlete specialising in ultra running triathlon rugby and boxing books publishededit year title publisher synopsis  hms brilliant bbc books the book describes the events that took place on the hms brilliant a royal navy frigate on front line duty in the adriatic during the yugoslavian war as part of operation sharp guard 00 shipmates century random house an exploration of the british royal navys heritage and its role in the modern world 00 commando arrow books random house chris terrills experience of training with the elite royal marines commandos and winning his own green beret before following them to the front line in afghanistan film historyedit year filmtelevision series broadcaster summary  subway inside story bbc crime and violence on the london underground 0 bullies 0 minutes bbc the chronic problem of school bullying 0 the race game inside story bbc an investigation into racism in british sport 0 fit to drop 0 minutes bbc the extraordinary story of people addicted to exercise  brief encounters 0 minutes bbc prostitutes pimps punters and the police at kings cross railway station  ape trade inside story special bbcnational geographic undercover investigation into international orangutan smuggling  yellow line inside story bbc the vicious parking wars on the streets of london  miami wild 0 minutes bbc policing the animal smuggling trade in florida  seeing red inside story bbc union unrest crime and violence on londons buses  the women trade inside story special bbc undercover investigation into international prostitution and the marketing of women for the sex industry  beloved country bbc part series on ordinary south african lives as the country approached full democracy and black rule  hms brilliant bbc part series on a royal navy warship serving during the yugoslavian war  alisons last mountain inside story special bbc journey to k with the family of alison hargreaves soon after her death on the mountain  soho stories bbc  part series about life in londons famous and flamboyant soho district  the cruise bbc  part series on board a luxury cruise ship in the caribbean featu